p.k: The Parent Teacher Association of Elmore Junior High ban video games, so the kids try and prove that games aren’t a bad influence. / Tobias follows every single high-five with a butt-slap, so when Gumball doesn’t get one he feels insulted. / Anais arrives in the bedroom to find a messy crime-scene and her Daisy doll missing. She realises that Gumball and Darwin are the chief suspects. / A mysterious figure from Nicole’s past shows up and challenges her to a fight, but the kids are surprised when she refuses. / A compilation of some of the funniest, most bizarre clips uploaded onto the internet by the people of Elmore.
